Backend Contract Summary for UI Integration

The UI calls one endpoint:

POST /api/agent/ask

Request:

{
  "message": "string",
  "userId": "user001",
  "sessionId": "recon-demo-session"
}

Response must always follow:

{
  "answer": "human readable AI answer",
  "userId": "user001",
  "sessionId": "recon-demo-session",
  "toolCalls": [
    {
      "toolName": "tool name",
      "toolResponse": {
        "result": {}
      }
    }
  ]
}

The UI uses:

answer = top narrative card
toolCalls[0].toolResponse.result = structured UI data

If only answer is returned and no tool data exists, UI shows a generic AI Answer screen.

