UI mapping
Backend field	UI usage
answer	Top card: Recommended Resolution
confidence	Confidence badge/gauge
likelyCauseCategory	Likely Cause card
errorSignature	Why / error signature text
recommendedNextSteps[]	Ordered action list
owner.team / owner.contact	Owner card
similarIncidents[]	Similar Incidents table
evidence[]	Evidence section; hide if empty
rcaDraft	RCA summary section
Important UI rules
If evidence is empty or null, UI hides the evidence button/section.
If similarIncidents is empty, UI shows “No similar incidents returned.”
owner must be rendered as fields, not as raw object.
confidence color:
0–30: red
31–70: amber
71–100: green
occurredOn should be ISO format if available.
Do not return placeholder strings like "string|null".
